Hello, welcome to [B]futurescape[/B]
This took me quite a while to edit [B] The is a new Boss![/B]
[B]Boss information[/B] This new Futurescape boss just looks like a ordinary white knight but know, This boss has 3000 Hitpoints and he hits 0's, But on a regular basis he hits from 1-99 usually 60-90. [B] How to get to the boss[/B] At draynor look for new Cave entrance i made,enter it and it will take you to the king black dragon lair,that is were the new boss is,(The cave is next to the pig den) [B] New Event[/B] New event you have to find a character that you have never seen before, if you get the correct one you get a rare snowball seed.
This server has no commands because this is an ecconemy server,!,!
Skills! -woodcutting -Theiving -Mining -Fishing -Prayer(lol) -attack(lol) -strength(lol) -defence(lol) -hitpoints (lol)
